{
  "dashboard": {
    "id": null,
    "title": "Centralized Logging Dashboard",
    "tags": ["logging", "loki", "logs", "observability"],
    "timezone": "browser",
    "panels": [
      {
        "id": 1,
        "title": "Log Volume Overview",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate({job=~\"$job\"}[$__interval])) by (job)",
            "legendFormat": "{{job}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {
            "unit": "reqps",
            "min": 0
          },
          {
            "unit": "short"
          }
        ],
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 8,
          "w": 12,
          "x": 0,
          "y": 0
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 2,
        "title": "Error Rate by Component",
        "type": "graph",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate({level=~\"ERROR|FATAL|CRITICAL\", job=~\"$job\"}[$__interval])) by (component)",
            "legendFormat": "{{component}}",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "yAxes": [
          {
            "unit": "reqps",
            "min": 0
          },
          {
            "unit": "short"
          }
        ],
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 8,
          "w": 12,
          "x": 12,
          "y": 0
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 3,
        "title": "Recent Error Logs",
        "type": "logs",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "{level=~\"ERROR|FATAL|CRITICAL\", job=~\"$job\"} |~ \"$search\" | line_format \"{{.component}}[{{.pod_name}}]: {{.message}}\"",
            "legendFormat": "",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showTime": true,
          "showLabels": false,
          "showCommonLabels": false,
          "wrapLogMessage": true,
          "prettifyLogMessage": true,
          "enableLogDetails": true,
          "dedupStrategy": "none",
          "sortOrder": "Descending"
        },
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 12,
          "w": 24,
          "x": 0,
          "y": 8
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 4,
        "title": "Application Logs Explorer",
        "type": "logs",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "{component=\"$component\", job=~\"$job\"} |~ \"$search\" | json | line_format \"[{{.level}}] {{.timestamp}} {{.message}}\"",
            "legendFormat": "",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showTime": true,
          "showLabels": true,
          "showCommonLabels": true,
          "wrapLogMessage": true,
          "prettifyLogMessage": true,
          "enableLogDetails": true,
          "dedupStrategy": "exact",
          "sortOrder": "Descending"
        },
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 12,
          "w": 12,
          "x": 0,
          "y": 20
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 5,
        "title": "Log Patterns Analysis",
        "type": "table",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(count_over_time({job=~\"$job\"} |~ \"$search\" [$__range])) by (level, component)",
            "legendFormat": "",
            "refId": "A",
            "instant": true
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "custom": {
              "displayMode": "color-text"
            },
            "mappings": [],
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "color": "green",
                  "value": null
                },
                {
                  "color": "yellow",
                  "value": 100
                },
                {
                  "color": "orange",
                  "value": 500
                },
                {
                  "color": "red",
                  "value": 1000
                }
              ]
            }
          },
          "overrides": [
            {
              "matcher": {
                "id": "byName",
                "options": "level"
              },
              "properties": [
                {
                  "id": "custom.displayMode",
                  "value": "color-background"
                },
                {
                  "id": "mappings",
                  "value": [
                    {
                      "options": {
                        "ERROR": {
                          "color": "red",
                          "index": 0
                        },
                        "WARN": {
                          "color": "orange",
                          "index": 1
                        },
                        "INFO": {
                          "color": "blue",
                          "index": 2
                        },
                        "DEBUG": {
                          "color": "gray",
                          "index": 3
                        }
                      },
                      "type": "value"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 8,
          "w": 12,
          "x": 12,
          "y": 20
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 6,
        "title": "Security Events",
        "type": "logs",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "{component=\"keycloak\"} |~ \"authentication.*failed|login.*failed|unauthorized|forbidden\" | line_format \"üîí SECURITY: {{.message}}\"",
            "legendFormat": "",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showTime": true,
          "showLabels": false,
          "showCommonLabels": false,
          "wrapLogMessage": true,
          "prettifyLogMessage": true,
          "enableLogDetails": true,
          "dedupStrategy": "none",
          "sortOrder": "Descending"
        },
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 8,
          "w": 12,
          "x": 0,
          "y": 28
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 7,
        "title": "Performance Issues",
        "type": "logs",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "{message=~\"timeout|slow|latency.*high|OutOfMemory|GC.*overhead\"} |~ \"$search\" | line_format \"‚ö° PERF: [{{.component}}] {{.message}}\"",
            "legendFormat": "",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showTime": true,
          "showLabels": false,
          "showCommonLabels": false,
          "wrapLogMessage": true,
          "prettifyLogMessage": true,
          "enableLogDetails": true,
          "dedupStrategy": "none",
          "sortOrder": "Descending"
        },
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 8,
          "w": 12,
          "x": 12,
          "y": 28
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 8,
        "title": "Business Logic Errors",
        "type": "logs",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "{component=\"scoring-api\", message=~\"business.*error|validation.*failed|constraint.*violation\"} | line_format \"üíº BUSINESS: {{.message}}\"",
            "legendFormat": "",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showTime": true,
          "showLabels": false,
          "showCommonLabels": false,
          "wrapLogMessage": true,
          "prettifyLogMessage": true,
          "enableLogDetails": true,
          "dedupStrategy": "none",
          "sortOrder": "Descending"
        },
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 8,
          "w": 12,
          "x": 0,
          "y": 36
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 9,
        "title": "Infrastructure Issues",
        "type": "logs",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "{component=~\"kafka|postgresql|redis\", level=~\"ERROR|WARN\"} |~ \"$search\" | line_format \"üèóÔ∏è INFRA: [{{.component}}] {{.message}}\"",
            "legendFormat": "",
            "refId": "A"
          }
        ],
        "options": {
          "showTime": true,
          "showLabels": false,
          "showCommonLabels": false,
          "wrapLogMessage": true,
          "prettifyLogMessage": true,
          "enableLogDetails": true,
          "dedupStrategy": "none",
          "sortOrder": "Descending"
        },
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 8,
          "w": 12,
          "x": 12,
          "y": 36
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 10,
        "title": "LogQL Query Builder",
        "type": "text",
        "options": {
          "content": "# üîç Requ√™tes LogQL Utiles\n\n## Recherche par niveau\n```\n{level=\"ERROR\"}\n{level=~\"WARN|ERROR\"}\n```\n\n## Recherche par composant\n```\n{component=\"scoring-api\"}\n{component=~\"kafka|postgresql\"}\n```\n\n## Recherche temporelle\n```\n{component=\"scoring-api\"} |= \"timeout\" | json\n```\n\n## Agr√©gation\n```\nsum(rate({level=\"ERROR\"}[5m])) by (component)\n```\n\n## Patterns complexes\n```\n{component=\"scoring-api\"} |~ \"user.*123.*error\" | json | user_id=`\"{{.user_id}}\"`\n```\n\n## Analyse de performance\n```\n{component=\"scoring-api\"} | json | latency > 5000\n```\n\n## S√©curit√©\n```\n{component=\"keycloak\"} |~ \"authentication.*failed\"\n```",
          "mode": "markdown"
        },
        "gridPos": {
          "h": 8,
          "w": 12,
          "x": 0,
          "y": 44
        }
      },
      {
        "id": 11,
        "title": "Log Metrics",
        "type": "stat",
        "targets": [
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate({job=~\"$job\"}[$__interval]))",
            "legendFormat": "Total Log Rate",
            "refId": "A"
          },
          {
            "expr": "sum(rate({level=\"ERROR\", job=~\"$job\"}[$__interval]))",
            "legendFormat": "Error Rate",
            "refId": "B"
          },
          {
            "expr": "count(sum(rate({job=~\"$job\"}[$__interval])) by (component))",
            "legendFormat": "Active Components",
            "refId": "C"
          }
        ],
        "fieldConfig": {
          "defaults": {
            "mappings": [],
            "thresholds": {
              "mode": "absolute",
              "steps": [
                {
                  "color": "green",
